        "text": "Analyze the provided image. You must respond ONLY with this exact JSON structure, no other format:\n\n{ \n  \"room_type\": \"...\",\n  \"decade_markers\": [...],\n  \"furniture\": [\"simple\", \"flat\", \"list\", \"of\", \"item\", \"names\"]\n  \"color_scheme\": {\n    \"dominant\": \"...\",\n    \"accents\": [...],\n    \"mood\": \"...\"\n  },\n  \"textures\": [...],\n  \"keywords\": [...]\n}\n\nDo not include URLs, titles, versions, or any other fields. JSON only.",
        "binaryPropertyName": "=data",
        "simplify": false,
        "options": {
          "system": "=You are analyzing a photograph of a household interior, likely from the 1970s or 1980s. The image ID is {{ $json.data.id }}.\n\nThe image has a dominant color tone of {{ $json.data.avg_color }}.\nPexels describes it as: \"{{ $json.data.alt }}\"\n\nPlease analyze the image and respond in the following exact JSON format:\n\n{ \"room_type\": \"the type of room (e.g. living room, kitchen, bedroom)\",\n  \"decade_markers\": [\"list\", \"of\", \"visual\", \"clues\", \"suggesting\", \"the\", \"era\"],\n  \"furniture\": [\"list\", \"of\", \"furniture\", \"items\", \"visible\"],\n  \"color_scheme\": {\n    \"dominant\": \"primary color or tone\",\n    \"accents\": [\"secondary\", \"colors\"],\n    \"mood\": \"one-word mood descriptor (e.g. warm, cool, earthy)\"\n  },\n  \"textures\": [\"carpet\", \"wallpaper\", \"wood\", \"etc\"],\n  \"keywords\": [\"flat\", \"list\", \"of\", \"all\", \"descriptive\", \"keywords\"]\n}\n\nRespond with JSON only. No explanation or preamble. You must identify:\n- At least 4 decade_markers\n- At least 5 furniture items\n- At least 6 keywords\n- At least 3 textures\n- Specific color names (e.g. \"harvest gold\" not just \"brown\")",
          "temperature": 0.3,
          "top_k": 40,
          "num_predict": 2048,
          "repeat_penalty": 1.1
        }
      },
