        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "=\n/no_think\nYou are a specialist in 20th century interior design and material culture.\n\nHere is a structured analysis of a SPECIFIC household interior photograph:\n\nRoom type: {{ $json.model_output.room_type }}\nDecade markers: {{ $json.model_output.decade_markers.join(', ') }}\nFurniture observed: {{ $json.model_output.furniture.join(', ') }}\nDominant color: {{ $json.model_output.color_scheme.dominant }}\nAccent colors: {{ $json.model_output.color_scheme.accents.join(', ') }}\nMood: {{ $json.model_output.color_scheme.mood }}\nTextures observed: {{ $json.model_output.textures.join(', ') }}\nPexels description: {{ $json.alt }}\nDominant color hex: {{ $json.avg_color }}\n\nGenerate keywords derived ONLY from the specific details listed above.\nDo NOT add period stereotypes, generic era assumptions, or items not mentioned above.\nEvery keyword must be traceable to something in the input data above.\n\nRespond ONLY with this exact JSON structure:\n{\n  \"keywords_functional\": [\"room function keywords based ONLY on observed furniture and layout\"],\n  \"keywords_aesthetic\": [\"style keywords ONLY from observed details\"],\n  \"keywords_material\": [\"ONLY materials and textures actually listed above\"],\n  \"keywords_era\": [\"ONLY decade markers listed above\"],\n  \"keywords_color\": [\"ONLY colors mentioned above, converted to period names where appropriate\"],\n  \"keywords_flat\": [\"deduplicated flat list of all keywords above\"]\n}\n\nJSON only. No preamble."
            }
          ]
        },
        "simplify": false,
        "options": {
          "temperature": 0.3,
          "top_k": 30,
          "num_predict": 2048,
          "repeat_penalty": 1.1
        }
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.ollama",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        144,
        192
      ],
      "id": "87a9e70b-7d54-4c25-83e8-4dfb5f99cea0",
      "name": "Message a model",
      "credentials": {
        "ollamaApi": {
          "id": "xwQDNdcxZ7ymLBxf",
          "name": "Ollama account 4"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
